[% PROCESS header.tt %]
<div id="header"><h1>Email Validation</h1></div>
<div id="content">
[% IF error %]
<p>[% error %]</p>
[% ELSE %]
<p>Please click on the link in the email we sent you to validate
your email, [%user.name%]. The email was sent to ([%user.email%]).</p>
[% END %]
<h2>Didn't receive an email?</h2>

Fill out the email address you want to use here:

<form action="[%c.uri_for('user/reconfirm')%]" method="POST">
<label for="email">email:<label> <input id="email" type="text" name="email"/>
<input type="submit" name="OK" value="OK"/>
</form>

<p>If you are unable to validate, please <a href="[%c.uri_for('logout')%]">log out</a>.</p>
</div>
        <div id="bottomnav">&nbsp;
[% PROCESS footer.tt %]
